66
00:05:03,345 --> 00:05:04,428
Selamat berkenalan.

67
00:05:04,429 --> 00:05:06,972
Kami akan menghabiskan waktu pagi menikmati pemandangan,

68
00:05:06,973 --> 00:05:08,766
