78
00:05:37,546 --> 00:05:39,171
Itu idea yang bagus. Jom guna pokok tu.

79
00:05:39,172 --> 00:05:40,464
Ia terkenal di Yangdong.

80
00:05:40,465 --> 00:05:43,676
Cik Song, tentang bahan yang anda hantar…

81
