90
00:06:21,923 --> 00:06:23,382
Mereka semua nakal.

91
00:06:24,467 --> 00:06:25,926
Adakah anda kalah?

92
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:28,013
- Kemudian saya akan memandu-- - Saya raja permainan.

93
00:06:28,763 --> 00:06:30,807
